name: Uth_Sulrowe
content: Doctor Uth Sulrowe was a Mon Calamari antiquities dealer who ran the Swain Import/Export Emporium in Cjaalysce'I on Socorro. A shrewd dealer and businessbeing, Sulrowe sized up all customers who entered the Emporium. Sulrowe's intuition helped her in the Emporium's real business; selling Caelli-Merced Syndicate weapons and equipment. Her senses have more than once detected Imperial operatives attempting to infiltrate Pret Swain's operations.
